    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT80-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">talaimakaṭkup pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpap parattai colliyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered by the other woman/courtesan to be heard by those who are close to HER.</p>
          </div>



        <div xml:id="KT80">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>                kūnta lāmpaṉ muḻuneṟi yaṭaiccip</l>
<l>                perumpuṉal vanta viruntuṟai virumpi</l>
<l>                yāmaḵ tayarkañ cēṟun tāṉaḵ</l>
<l>                tañcuva tuṭaiya ḷāyiṉ vempōr</l>
<l>                nukampaṭak kaṭakkum palvē leḻiṉi</l>
<l>                muṉaiyāṉ perunirai pōlak</l>
<l>                kiḷaiyoṭuṅ kākkataṉ koḻunaṉ mārpē.</l>
             </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent">Whole calyxes of waterlily put in [our] tresses,</l>
          <l rend="indent">desirous of the dark ghat where the great flood has come</l>
          <l>we shall go to immerse ourselves there.</l>
          <l rend="indent">If she is possessed by fear of that</l>
          <l>she may guard her husband, together with [her] relatives too,</l>
          <l>like many-speared Eḻiṉi, with big rows on the [battle-]front,</l>
          <l>who conquers [enemies] in hot battle to bear [his] yoke.</l>
          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="5+6b">
            <l>just as many-speared Eḻiṉi who conquers ...</l>
              <l>[guards] a big herd of cows on the [battle-]front.</l>
          </lg>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
